7.B)Create sample Supplier table SupId,SupName,SupPhone - Orders table Orderid,OrderDate,Supplierid
A). create table Supplier(
        SupId varchar(10) primary key,
        SupName varchar(50),
        SupPhone varchar(20)
    );
    create table Orders(
        OrderId varchar(10) primary key,
        OrderDate date,
        SupplierId varchar(10),
        foreign key (SupplierId) references Supplier(SupId)
    );
8)  Create a query to fetch the data joining Supplier table and Orders table (innerjoin)
